                Biokinetix is the psytrance project of
                Fabrice Leborgne from France. After some
                releases on digital and CD compilations in
                the past two years, his full album is finally
                landing on Morphonic records! With his
                energetic music style, the performances of
                Biokinetix had already acquired a strong
                popularity on many countries in Europe
                including Russia, Portugal, Italy or France.

                This album is a new step up for Biokinetix,
                confirming his name as a reference for crazy
                dancing nights, creating hysteria among the
                psytrance floors worldwide! This album
                presents his vision of the current
                centuryHeavy, full of energy and high-tech
                sounds, but with also a touch of humour,
                Including refined production tricks, smashing
                breaks and driving basslines. This album
                features also some successful collaborations
                with artists like Mesmerizer, DSP, Beatrave,
                including an aerial last track with LDB from
                Secret Vibes. All tracks were then sublimed
                by the mastering from XSI. The 21st century
                must surely counting with the name of
                Biokinetix!
